di luar imajinasimu.

188
00:11:09.450 --> 00:11:10.730
Bagus!

189
00:11:12.600 --> 00:11:15.500
Ibu meninggalkan dia?

190
00:11:16.970 --> 00:11:18.170
Ya.

191
00:11:19.270 --> 00:11:20.980
Aku meninggalkannya.

